<p class="ql-align-center">一提起战争</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家都是<strong>战战兢兢目光如炬憋着屎憋着尿</strong>的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说到底</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是紧脏严肃的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/a32e79523e114b4e84cb4f26255aabed.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">史上有些战争理由还是很<strong>奇葩</strong>的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就跟朕平时玩大富翁游戏一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>既紧脏又儿戏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕就来说说中外战争那些奇葩的理由</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200928/e81d374b0ac1431d860b61d82fc5e274.gif" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
