<h1 class="ql-align-center">01</h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">穷鬼之战</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>打我吧！我太穷了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>周厉王</strong>时期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">王室衰微</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>楚王熊渠</strong>趁机作乱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">攻打<strong>随国</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随国觉得莫名其妙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200928/169a3b7b442849e2982a727af22148fd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当时<strong>蛮夷</strong>在长江流域一带</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仗着又远又穷又落后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">周王懒得管</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">楚王干脆不遵守中原的规矩和礼仪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>想打谁就打谁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还收获了江汉一带人民的<strong>拥戴</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200928/1e3e30104c274f1dbf8b5d159d279172.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">02</h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">茅草之战</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>决斗吧！因为你欠人锤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出来横总是要还的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">周王室解体后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">齐国就是楚国的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>报应</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这事还要从蔡国说起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200928/100184a968974d1f8ba89f3d61e5d5d4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了讨好齐国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>蔡穆侯</strong>将妹妹<strong>蔡姬</strong>嫁给<strong>齐桓公小白</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">组成了<strong>老夫少妻组合</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小白格外宠爱蔡姬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有一天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们去划船</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>旱鸭子</strong>小白天生晕船</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让她不要摇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">少女总是<strong>叛逆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摇得更厉害了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200928/dfff472b2ee0421994b75b51975a8088.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一气之下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小白直接送她回蔡国老家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">面壁思过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200928/0913e1c0c5764ee383e45daed26fbb68.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">误以为妹妹<strong>被退货</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蔡王面子挂不住</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一怒之下把妹妹<strong>转嫁给楚王</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200928/3d436d16318a43b893bb7e3a9ec83fb9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当时小白还没休妻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一听见老婆<strong>擅自改嫁</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">立马组织八国联军出兵蔡国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把蔡国干趴下了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一报<strong>绿帽之仇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200928/e74e7bfc85114465a3367d8cef2c36f9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这还没完</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小白赶紧带着蔡国打楚国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此时楚国<strong>一脸懵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200928/3943fc78f391430ba1de7be41f03cfa9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搁在今日</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这理由确实弱爆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200928/8845a85ed8484c3dbf0b40e66499fe85.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当时周王室认为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白茅能通灵，是祭祀必备品</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">楚国作为<strong>白茅免费供应商</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不按时交货就是藐视周王</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阻碍祭祀就是藐视礼乐制度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>等同造反</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">起兵合情合理</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">实在没想到楚成王会<strong>乖乖顺从</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">架没打成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小白又想了一招</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200928/d93ffeac7f2a4ac796bb0fcc22c59343.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这理由更狗碎了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">昭王南征都过去<strong>300多年</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">先不说昭王是不是来楚国了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">消失时齐国不来找</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现在才来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摆明是来<strong>找茬的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/d562921d1a7f4dada33617695631cb39.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">03</h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">桑叶之战</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>桑叶的落下，是风的不挽留，还是隔壁太手欠！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>楚国地大招坑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>齐国坑完吴国坑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">话说吴楚边界刚好有一棵<strong>桑树</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">桑叶长在哪国就属于哪国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两国采桑妇女摘得好好的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可有一天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吴国妇女为了摘多点桑叶就越了<strong>三八界</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">楚国妇女维权赶人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吴人拒不出去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>两国妇女直接骂街</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还招来父老乡亲一起开骂</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200928/68bfaa2b3685436e8c7854ea1984d460.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打着打着楚人还把<strong>军队</strong>招来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打得吴国桑叶帮措手不及</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>吴王僚</strong>听了还得了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>——直接出兵报仇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>正好夺了楚国两座城池</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200928/bdd26082201f4f559d676c505df7a617.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">04</h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">一口酒之战</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你送我的酒没有他的好，偏心！开打吧！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然被白茅和桑叶坑了两回</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可楚国也<strong>不是善茬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有一次</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>楚宣王</strong>组了个酒局</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">欢迎各国来喝酒蹦迪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">去别人家要带礼物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赵国送了好酒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而鲁国偏偏送了<strong>薄酒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本来赵国把酒送上去就完事了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">偏偏此时楚国官员向赵人<strong>索贿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赵人拒不给钱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">官员使坏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将赵国好酒和鲁国薄酒掉包</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">楚宣王喝了薄酒后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">认定赵王故意挑衅找茬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接出兵<strong>赵国首都</strong>——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>邯郸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200928/f5df93b7c62c4486ba1f844d53bd2b57.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样看下来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">周朝各国打仗理由</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也<strong>太朴</strong>（粗）<strong>素</strong>（暴）了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟人家处于奴隶社会末期嘛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还带着<strong>野人的淳</strong>（暴）<strong>朴</strong>（力）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“淳朴”是<strong>会传染的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中世纪和近代的欧美洲混战理由</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更是一股清流</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如，为了一撮胡子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200928/f06fb7a1a36e4f6196421af6b6491b9d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200928/7105ea21f47347c8939111eba9b86b0a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">05</h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">胡须之战</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>性感国王，在线蓄胡，蓄到民政厅</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凭着<strong>一撮迷人胡须</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>路易七世</strong>和法国公爵的女儿<strong>艾丽诺</strong>结婚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个是法兰西国王</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个是法国公爵的女儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">路易得到了<strong>法国南部两个省的陪嫁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200928/53b5c78a2b9643419c2638e726cb16d4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200928/f36ac581f9d74db9bf9e5dcce67dea25.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从<strong>十字军</strong>退役后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">路易就剃掉了胡子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">艾丽诺嫌弃他没有胡子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>很</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>难</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>看</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后离了婚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还改嫁英国国王<strong>亨利二世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对路易来说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">离婚倒没什么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200928/c8c18500e8294b6fabb09f75791c09ea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可气的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">前妻要求<strong>将两个省的嫁妆转交给她的新老公</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200928/eae9fb9faa4148e4aa0618ec7b40d232.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">路易偏不交</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">亨利决定以<strong>武力夺取嫁妆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出兵法国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">战争一打就是301年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200928/f5e6a84d94a34a5491d1edfd1045b15b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">06</h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">猪之战</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>打狗还得看主人，打猪也一样！瞄准！射击！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了一撮胡子开战只是个例</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">近代欧洲主要为了资源抢破头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>美英差点因为一头猪开战</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">1846年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英美双方签订了<strong>《俄勒冈条约》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">解决了领土划分问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200928/f36ac581f9d74db9bf9e5dcce67dea25.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搞笑的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无意中又制造了一个新的领土纠纷：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>两国都认为</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>圣胡安小岛是属于自己的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了夺得先机</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国人在岛上设立了<strong>食物中转站</strong>和<strong>牧羊场</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">美国人则<strong>登岛定居度假</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两国暗中占地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一国占一半</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁也不让谁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200928/75b19c702d8541cc96330ebe10a64d56.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直到1859年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">美国人<strong>卡尔</strong>在岛上度假时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打死了来自<strong>英国牧羊场的猪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">猪主人要求杀猪凶手赔100美元</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不赔就报警</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当时人均才<strong>几美元工资</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">100美元简直勒索</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200928/4a8af39ccad84e588de946c9519b9afd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杀猪凶手<strong>拒不赔偿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还说猪踩烂了自己的马铃薯地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">向美国当局求救</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当局派了一个<strong>小兵团</strong>助阵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">猪主人也向英国女王求救</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">女王不甘示弱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">派了<strong>3艘军舰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200928/f0ebf1db1295477ab35f1a3c0e25874d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">短短2个月</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">岛上美军增加到<strong>461人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">配了<strong>14门大炮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英军则出动了<strong>5艘军舰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2140名士兵</strong>以及<strong>70门火炮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两国伺机而动……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200928/704b1eec8738499a85784d9bf6ada9b9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但冷静下来后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两国都觉得为一只猪战斗<strong>很愚蠢</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后和解</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这场宣而未打的猪之战</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>最终仅以一头猪的伤亡为代价宣告结束</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/98c8846bcb9341539426298aa8346a62.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">07</h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">龙虾之战</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>为了证明龙虾是游的还是爬的，他们开炮了！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">猪是跑的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以判定是哪一国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可龙虾就不好说了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>它是爬行还是游泳？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个问题<strong>既无聊又关键</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟涉及到一国的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">领海权</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>1961年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一群法国渔民去巴西沿海地区捞鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一网下去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果捞上来一大堆<strong>龙虾</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">巴西人不乐意了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本来龙虾量就少</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法国人还来抢自家门口的龙虾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两国渔民吵了起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200928/cb1d980aa99649f8a1a7d773a3091800.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当时法国人捞到的龙虾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正好在巴西的专属经济区内</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200928/84fc993384cc424bb5ea594388d00f9c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当时<strong>《联合国海洋法公约》</strong>还没出生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并没有专属经济区这个概念！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200928/8ac751f7686f4240871d75f44c2151dc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双方出动了<strong>军舰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">巴西派<strong>一艘</strong>（谁也别想从我这捞走一只龙虾！）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法国则派出了<strong>一个编队</strong>…</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双方在海上对峙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是这样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两国为<strong>“龙虾是游的还是爬的”</strong>杠了2年…</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直到1982年《联合国海洋法公约》出生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200928/a87f62336e7e49a8a4143ced07e88783.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为资源和领土开战是在所难免的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但又为了资源停战</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个理由有点儿…特别…</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/05914c7d4b784cbcb5c5ad16533b6c4b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200928/768137c9d2714cc0969e7aa5fbd9b793.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">08</h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">土豆之战</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>暂停开炮！我先收个土豆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">1777年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">统治巴伐利亚的<strong>维特尔斯巴赫王朝</strong>绝后了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">继承权落在了近亲<strong>卡尔</strong>手里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/99055093ac9a4332bd82e71ca22c8024.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他对皇位一点兴趣也没有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200928/b3e90df33e3a4e91a6b90011650aaa15.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>人淡如菊</strong>的他</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不想管那么大地方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">决定<strong>割让下巴伐利亚给奥地利</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200928/74644fcca2714c7791a6cd55f61d1aeb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这么大的免费午餐谁能错过？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两方在签约前一刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>普鲁士</strong>大喊“刀下留地”杀出来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">奥地利得到下巴伐利亚必然会威胁普鲁士的霸权</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">与其躺着被打</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">普鲁士决定<strong>主动出兵奥地利</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200928/4418e96121c240ce9559bac3812d7887.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双方打到波西米亚地区时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正好是<strong>土豆成熟季节</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双方一边对峙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一边忙着收割马铃薯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">另一种说法是双方互扔马铃薯作为武器</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总之</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">马铃薯阻止了一场大规模战争</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/559ed386c8154ed9a0237443537d390e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">事情是这样的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">17、18世纪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">欧洲人民正好碰上<strong>小冰河时期</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">引发饥荒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">得亏马铃薯早熟又高产</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成了<strong>救命法宝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以战争在马铃薯面前根本不值一提</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200928/e0e13b987890454dad3862d42ae42e82.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">09</h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">打卡式之战</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>白天轰轰轰，晚上吨吨吨，只有战斗民族干得出这事</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">马铃薯作为停战理由还挺<strong>别致</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当然</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有更奇葩的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>摩尔多瓦</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苏联的成员国之一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苏联解体后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摩尔多瓦开始考虑自己跟谁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当时的总统<strong>希望投入罗马尼亚的怀抱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而斯拉夫人民<strong>则想回归乌克兰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是决定脱离摩尔多瓦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">独立建国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>1992年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">内战一触即发</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一开始摩尔多瓦政府军3000多人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">斯拉夫仅800多人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两方都是拿步枪<strong>砰砰砰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后来斯拉夫搞来了坦克<strong>轰轰轰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200928/cf17a8bfcf0e4937b42d61455d212685.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">原来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">斯拉夫大妈团怕人多欺负人少</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>用身体做路障</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">去劫沙俄的坦克</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沙俄故意<strong>放水</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">撮合斯拉夫轰轰轰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200928/761a4290c7334b0095b8a747fb9b800c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白天打仗归打仗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晚上夜生活还是要兼顾的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双方默契决定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白天轰轰轰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晚上聚在酒馆吨吨吨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">喝酒跳舞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果哪个战友不幸白天战死了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晚上大家还会一起<strong>举杯悼念</strong>……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这不就是欧洲版的杯酒释军权嘛…</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200928/b6e376a83ecd4a0881fedcf6567677bc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对于平凡百姓来说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哪怕战争理由再奇葩再好笑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打你的那一天肯定笑不出来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕只想活着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>朕想吃的东西还没吃够呢！！！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200928/114a51798c8a42eda607614dd95da0d3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
